channel.title: Quick question
channel.description: Ok, after downloading Uncalled attack v4 (great release and server btw) I was going to make a few changes. But when i compile it gives the regular "recompile with -Xlint" thing. But in most cases it still compiles. But mine won't compile at all, and it wont change anything. I see now that is loading the .jar files from one of the folders. But i have no clue on how to change those... Any help?
